name: BlackRockCountdown
0:
”Alexa, ask Black Rock Countdown when does the man burn?”
”Alexa, ask Black Rock Countdown when do the gates open up?”

Invocation Name: black rock countdown
des:
Excited for Burning Man? This skill is the unofficial countdown to when the gates open on the Playa and when the man burns! See you on the Playa!
